msgctxt "Deku_Cancel00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A hundred years ago, you would have\n"
"been able to pull out the sword easily.\n"
"You have grown weak.\n"
"You must find a way to become stronger.<2.pa>\n"
"<3.so>Ho ho ho..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It would seem you still lack the\n"
"necessary strength for this task. \n"
"You must recommit to your training."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (long)
#. 2: sound2
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel01_2"
msgid ""
"...However, you were quite close this\n"
"time.<1.pa> <2.so>Ho ho ho..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ho ho ho...<2.pa> Why so fearful?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Your strength is greater now than it was\n"
"a century ago. All you need now is the\n"
"determination to succeed."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: sound2
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You still lack the necessary strength.<2.pa>\n"
"But it doesn't look like you lack for\n"
"training. No...\n"
"Perhaps you imagine...<3.pa>that the\n"
"containers given to you by the statues\n"
"of the Goddess cannot be changed?\n"
"Visit Hateno Village in the southeast of\n"
"Hyrule. There you will find one who\n"
"trades in such containers.\n"
"Though...he is a bit wicked...<4.pa>\n"
"<5.so>Ho ho ho..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You still lack the necessary strength.<2.pa>\n"
"But it doesn't look like you lack for\n"
"training. No...\n"
"Offer a statue of the Goddess your\n"
"Spirit Orbs, and try increasing the hearts\n"
"that make up your true strength."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You think you can pull out the sword\n"
"while suffering such injuries?! Heal your\n"
"wounds first, or you stand no chance."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Deku_Cancel06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ho ho...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Why so fearful?<2.pa> Come back and try again\n"
"once you've found your determination."
msgstr ""

